FestivalPlanner.GUI.AgendaGUI.PopUpGUI

Class AbstractCreationPopUp

  • java.lang.Object
    • FestivalPlanner.GUI.AbstractGUI
      • FestivalPlanner.GUI.AgendaGUI.PopUpGUI.AbstractCreationPopUp
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AboutPopUp, ArtistPopUp, PodiumPopUp

    public abstract class AbstractCreationPopUp
extends AbstractGUI
    Abstract class used by creation window PopUps such as ArtistPopUp and PodiumPopUp.

    This class contains methods with filled bodies, whom call abstract methods. This way extending this class is quite flexible to ensure an efficient and relatively fast workflow. Examples:

    • load() calls abstract method additionalLoad().
    • setup() calls abstract method additionalSetup().
    • actionHandlingSetup() calls abstract method additionalActionHandlingSetup().

    Furthermore, this class contains attributes for stage width and height, to ensure consistency in our graphical user interface.
